# NF PR conflict resolver — mandatory

**Law:** `docs/ops/NF_PR_CONFLICT_RESOLVER_LOCKED_v1.md` · **R-013**  
**Skill:** `.cursor/skills/SKILL-011-pr-conflict-resolver.md`  
