## Before resolving any PR conflict

1. Load SKILL-011 + upstream `sina-governance-SSOT/skills/pr-conflict-resolver/SKILL.md` §0–§1
2. Classify each conflicted file: `python3 scripts/nf_pr_conflict_classify_v1.py --git`
3. Never blind text-merge `data/*.json`, receipts, or `*LOCKED*.md`

## Before claiming merge-ready

```bash
python3 scripts/verify_pr_conflict_resolver_v1.py
```

